Here's an updated example with `word-break: break-word`:

```css
p {
  white-space: pre-wrap;
  word-wrap: break-word;
  word-break: break-word;
  max-width: 300px;
  line-height: 1.2em;
}
```

This should help prevent words from being cut off in the middle and instead breaking the word at a point where it can fit on the next line. 

